{"tid":1454000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"dpark俾防暴入場就咁算？","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T06:41:04.000Z","uid":107178,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"965ec876476cdfb9be0b40d34d286171faeb4328","tid":1454000,"uid":107178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:54:33.000Z","msg":"愉景新城比防暴入<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1440920\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1440920</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Me68g2i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMe68g2i.png&h=58592751&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDpark解釋<br />\n<br />\n有關防暴警察未有通知下進入商場使用洗手間<br />\n<br />\n對於今晚(2019年8月10日)有防暴警察在事前未有通知、在場亦有大批家庭顧客情況下忽然進入商場，愉景新城商場管理處表示遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n今晚10點04分，有數名警察從美環街入口進入商場，他們在使用最就近的洗手間五分鐘後，全部迅速離開。商場保安人員得悉他們進場後，已即時上前交涉，但警察表示有急切生理需要，他們使用洗手間後已即時離開商場。<br />\n<br />\n對於因為有數名警察忽然出現，可能令部分顧客或商戶感到憂慮，愉景新城商場管理處對此深感抱歉。商場已即時加派工作人員維持場內秩序。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但點解</span><br />\n1. 警署同消防局就喺隔離，要去商場廁所？<br />\n2. Dpark聲稱由美環街入口入，而商場搞泊車counter對正美環街入口，咁都唔可以即時反應？<br />\n3. 睇下張相，兩隻狗嘅姿勢係企定定咁款，似去/去完廁所？商場會唔會有cctv片證明真係五分鐘後走左？<br />\n4. 班狗竟然葵芳地鐵站室內放催淚彈，商場會唔會有任何措施去保障客人安全？<br />\n<br />\n今日有狗「擅自」入場，會唔會有一日變新城市2.0？<br />\n作為主打細路同家庭客嘅商場，未有合理解釋&amp;預防措拖前，一直追問落去，唔好俾件事淡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YseBqYh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYseBqYh.png&h=5ce181e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日人入機場！<br />\n打電話追問爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">宜家唔係普通軍裝入黎借廁所啊<br />\n係綠衫防暴啊屌<br />\n可能有過期Tear gas殘留係衫上面<br />\n而佢地走左入一個普通市民嘅商場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪警署落撚左閘搞到你兩隻狗要去人嘅廁所啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"baf9f2c59f27c490aeec5d1cf5858914d0e53831","tid":1454000,"uid":107178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:55:03.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"d6c01618ed18c73a7d892892aacc7cae1870f4d7","tid":1454000,"uid":107178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:55:18.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"983344b4c31cc2e94daed4cfaf8cf2c23e586274","tid":1454000,"uid":107178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:56:08.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"5bbf60b3f75224275f4627965b566949ef7acd45","tid":1454000,"uid":26441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:56:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa1153c0cb6650352d6c51f9ebe5642f650dd520","tid":1454000,"uid":107178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:56:23.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"16dc065912213380ff11ca2249dbb60444617a48","tid":1454000,"uid":107178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:57:01.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"25c6e082ed2036fc9a6ec90fc6ec3067fab005e4","tid":1454000,"uid":107178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:57:34.000Z","msg":"一個都唔好放過<br />\n要佢出聲明譴責班狗不請自來"},{"pid":"bc24c52c85e950851ad7bad853d757370366a0be","tid":1454000,"uid":107178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:58:59.000Z","msg":"係防暴啊<br />\n殘留過期tear gas帶埋入商場<br />\n屌佢老母"},{"pid":"821fa1ad509590482a859c9de88e657b0ff679d2","tid":1454000,"uid":279348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:59:07.000Z","msg":"睇錯左以為係 DPRK........"},{"pid":"a69ce9cd6c0b5e1f4e2d5f7f973c1a1bac75c780","tid":1454000,"uid":34990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:59:48.000Z","msg":"之前仲出聲明話唔比差佬入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b68987ed4cc19d5ad83f51c8e63c2e9f0827017","tid":1454000,"uid":107178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:59:49.000Z","msg":"Dpark仲想做家庭客生意嘅唔該出一份正式聲明"},{"pid":"d3869ef3b44e889c189d37800e6525d98dbe6a05","tid":